---
title: Rainbow Haloumi & Chicken Bowl with Chipotle Slaw, Charred Corn & Garlic Aioli
description: Let’s fill the bowl to the brim with salty golden slices of haloumi, chicken, a sweetcorn salsa and a chipotle sauce slaw with a hit of lime to add a dash of zest and tang. Tonight will be bursting with both colour and flavour
